node.text:
Follow @the.frenchdiver for more.

📽 @elhamgholami
Rainbow Island, Iran 🇮🇷 The soil composing Hormuz Island in #Iran is highly concentrated with Iron Oxide. This concentration leads to red coloration, which is washed up in the waves.
Have you ever seen anything like this?

📍 Hormuz, Iran

node.text:
Welcome to paradise at Calilo, a tranquil retreat via @adrianbaias with @florina__toma 😍 Get your photos posted in our account, apply for a feature visiting tourfervor.com 👉🏼 the link is in our bio: @tourfervor

A visionary conservation project that offers an escape from the clamour and the crowds. Think sun-drenched seclusion surrounded by an ancient olive-pricked landscape - @nature and art at its heart. Find yourself and all you need in a land in deep connection with everything.

Who would you share this hideout with? 😌

📽 @adrianbaias w/ @florina__toma
📍 Calilo Hotel, Ios, Greece
🎶 Henry Mancini - Lujon

Is this the most beautiful mantis in @nature? 🙏 Get your photos posted in our account, apply for a feature visiting tourfervor.com 👉🏼 the link is in our bio: @tourfervor

Flower mantises are those species of praying mantises that mimic flowers. Their coloration is an example of aggressive mimicry, a form of camouflage in which a predator's colours and patterns lure prey.

📽 @insecthaus_adi

This is Switzerland 🇨🇭😍 Share your photos with us and we will post them in our account. Apply for a feature following the link in our bio: @tourfervor

Tag someone you’d like to explore these places with!

Videos by & locations at:
1. @amir_asani13 - Stechelberg
2. @emrije.a - Uri
3. @sennarelax - Meiringen
4. @khadija_sweetheart - Lungern
5. @aventouro - Lenk
6. @zadizadi.life - Saxer Lücke
7. @doounias - Canton Schwyz
8. @switzerland_by_marc - St Moritz
9. @life_of_fab27 - Unterschächen
10. @michelphotographych - Lauterbrunnen
